Date November 2020 Marks available 1 Reference code 20N.1.SL.TZ0.22
Level Standard level Paper Paper 1 Time zone TZ0 / no time zone
Command term Question number 22 Adapted from N/A

Question

An animal has the following characteristics: bilateral symmetry, mouth but no anus, ribbon shape. Which phylum does the animal belong to?

A. Mollusca

B. Cnidaria

C. Annelida

D. Platyhelmintha

Markscheme

D
